extendedInfo.description: THE ESSENTIAL ROCK AND ROLL REFERENCE APP!Over 2100 artists in current and past rock, pop and music history detailed in this reference app. Artists are sorted by birthday with quick searching by date or artist name. Each artist also has details on age, date of death, birthplace and link to Wikipedia entry for thousands of pages of rock history, trivia, discographies, and more.Touch screen functionality lets you easily navigate dates and views with flicks and clicks of the finger on your favourite Android device.This app is certified ad-ware free.

reviews.title: Wrong dates?
reviews.comment: I\'m finding that birth dates and ages are not matching with actual fact.. other than that it\'s a cool app.
reviews.author: A Google User
